items.sentence: All of us except for Tom thought Mary was guilty.
Anything that is too stupid to be spoken is sung.
Tom certainly can\'t become a member of our club.
Tom certainly doesn\'t seem to mind helping Mary.
Tom certainly isn\'t as smart as he thinks he is.
Please get your report to me as soon as possible.
Please take your time before deciding what to do.
We thought that we wouldn\'t be able to stop Tom.
I\'ve been trying to imagine my life without you.
I\'ve got more money than I know what to do with.
